<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="arrest-vt">arrest <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'rest/    美 /ə'rest/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>逮捕；拘留：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A man has been arrested and is being questioned now.
一名男子已被逮捕，正在接受审问。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My brother was <strong>arrested for</strong> drunk driving. 
我哥哥因为酒后驾车被拘留。</p></div></div>